Package: rserve-sandbox-docker
Architecture: amd64
# https://stackoverflow.com/questions/38728693/cannot-install-docker-on-debian-jessie
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, bash (>= 4.3), r-base, r-base-dev, docker.io
Description: Docker spec for running Rserve in a sandbox
 This directory builds a docker image based on
 Debian that safely executes Rserve.
 .
 The Rserve instance is made available as /home/rserve/socket.

